The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Metro Recommends

 THE DVD 

 (MusicWorld, Rs 595)

 The ex-Pink Floyd singer and guitarist performs classics like Shine on You Crazy Diamond, Coming Back to Life and Comfortably Numb live in 2001 and 2002 concerts. Bonus material includes a ?spare digits? section for a close-up of Gilmour?s fingers during guitar solos. 

 THE DISPLAY

 (UZ 213 Swabhumi, 12 noon to 8.30 pm, till January 31) The lifetstyle show features Bengal pottery at its best. Participating artists are Arun Mukhoty, Gourab Malakar, Manik Das, Manoj Kumar Das, Mousumi Roy, Payel Sarkar, Partha Dasgupta, Soumen Basu and Tanmoy Das. Presented by Arts and Ideas.

 THE CARNIVAL

 (Swabhumi, December 15, 16 and 17)

 The three-daylong fest-cum-carnival features loads of contests for schoolchildren ? from creative writing to T-shirt painting, tug of war, music, street play, sudoku, antakshari and much more.




